  </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><u>Project Cost: </u>Not exceed Rs. 50 <span class="SpellE">lac</span> (including margin money for working capital).<u><o:p></o:p></u></p>
  <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:
  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal;mso-list:
