  </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><u>Promoters’ Contribution:</u> Minimum 10<span class="GramE">%<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>of</span> project cost.<u><o:p></o:p></u></p>
  <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:
